		hmtsHfcPatchOperation OBJECT-TYPE
			SYNTAX OCTET STRING
			MAX-ACCESS read-write
			STATUS current
			DESCRIPTION
				"Get: Returns currently supported operations (bit field) 
				Example 01 06
				  0x01 : count of operation features bytes
				  0x06 : 0x02 = always high (this get operation supported)
				  0x04 = reset transponder counters operation supported (-> operation 0x02)
				  Tip: operation number can be solved by shifting bits toward BIT0.            
				
				Set values:
				  0x02 = resets HFC packet counters (Queries, Failures (%), Cont. failures)    
				
				"
			::= { hmtsMIB 8 }

		
